{"author":{"id":"783b610f274a0d93f6239db0fc75d0982606c877a4661d3aea84b42bc3a85cea"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1520386018,"nonce":"BNTVTXqWtBRw/Lumqg7usgXnjOM=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDM3MDk4OTk1Mw==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/1754#issuecomment-370989953"},"message":"Changing metadata for multiple datasets at once is another enhancement idea that started with one request and had more activity/ideas added by others. https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/issues/3195 Right now the option is to either edit attributes per-dataset or reload. \n\nI really like the pop-up \"Did you forget to set this?\" upload GUI idea from Dan. Some tool forms already have this for required settings that are NOT set at job submission (users are warned before the job is launched - saves compute and troubleshooting-an-error time). Upload is a different kind of tool, but some warnings/help in there would be nice. It is pretty tricky to find some options (convert spaces to tabs could be more obvious, too - and only allow use with tabular type data, never with any datatype that has headers (I see that mistake a few times a month).\n\nThe tool filter _could_ be constructed so that BAMs with \"?\" assigned as the database are permitted to select any reference annotation. But make that an active choice still. And if a BAM does have a dbkey assigned, only permit the select if it is a match. This wouldn't be as strict - and is not my favorite solution. \n\nPeople map against the wrong database by accident and don't find out until they get odd results or a failure with a downstream tool. Ticket for an enhancement to prevent that is here: https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/issues/4499\n\nDan might have other ideas about how to model this. If there is are ways to prevent common usage mistakes upfront, I'm all for them. We can't prevent everything but a few extra tips/warnings would definitely help.","files":null},{"type":3,"timestamp":1522345586,"nonce":"P5xMyO9hO59VKfPcvox0qry8nFk=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDM3NzMxNjcxOQ==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/1754#issuecomment-377316719"},"message":"Featurecounts v 1.6.0.3 test well at htps://usegalaxy.org against all of the usage problems that can come up plus with correct inputs. Thank you!!  Closing.","files":null},{"type":4,"timestamp":1522345586,"nonce":"tgAFlLR4MT5Jku/DsP/Xa25/MSA=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDExOkNsb3NlZEV2ZW50MTU0ODQzOTIxMw=="},"status":2}]}